'''岩豚鼠屬'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Kerodon''}}）是[[水豚亞科|水豚亞科]]下的一個屬，其下生物是生活在[[南美洲|南美洲]]的[[齧齒動物|齧齒動物]]，與[[水豚屬|水豚屬]]生物有親緣關係。<ref name=msw3>{{MSW3 Woods|id=13400220}}</ref>它們主要生活在巖石嶙峋的峭壁上和洞穴中，也因此得名。<ref name="White">{{cite web|last=White|first=Alex|title=Kerodon rupestris|url=http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/accounts/Kerodon_rupestris/#physical_description|publisher=Animal Diversity Web|accessdate=30 September 2013|archive-date=2014-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011001016/http://animaldiversity.ummz.umich.edu/accounts/Kerodon_rupestris/#physical_description|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==特徵==
他們的體型相對水豚要小得多，外形與兔子肖似、腳掌厚實。成年的岩豚鼠體長{{convert|20|-|40|cm}}，重約{{convert|1|kg}}。<ref name="Rock Cavy">{{cite web|title=Rock Cavy|url=http://www.centralpark.com/guide/central-park-zoo/rock-cavy.html|publisher=Central Park Zoo|accessdate=30 September 2013|archive-date=2017-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171013052112/http://www.centralpark.com/guide/central-park-zoo/rock-cavy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>主要以樹葉、樹皮、種子和草為食。<ref name="White"/>其懷孕期約76天，每年產胎1至3只，幼體在33天之內就會斷奶。133天後達到性成熟。<ref>{{cite web|title=Cavies and Maras: Caviidae - Rock Cavy (kerodon Rupestris): Species Accounts|url=http://animals.jrank.org/pages/3455/Cavies-Maras-Caviidae-ROCK-CAVY-Kerodon-rupestris-SPECIES-ACCOUNTS.html|publisher=Net Industries|accessdate=30 September 2013|archive-date=2015-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412132640/http://animals.jrank.org/pages/3455/Cavies-Maras-Caviidae-ROCK-CAVY-Kerodon-rupestris-SPECIES-ACCOUNTS.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==習性==
與近親[[水豚屬|水豚屬]]相同，岩豚鼠屬的生物高度社會化，<ref name="rowe">Rowe, D. L. and R. L. Honeycutt. 2002. Phylogenetic relationships, ecological correlates, and molecular evolution within the Cavioidea (Mammalia, Rodentia). Molecular Biology and Evolution, 19:263-277.</ref>族群中以雌性居多，雄性處於領導地位，且等級分明。通過不斷發出聲進行交流，因而這個群體顯得十分喧鬧。<ref name="Rock Cavy"/>雄性會佔領一個或者數個岩地作為自己的領土，在傍晚時候開始活躍。<ref>{{cite web|title=Cavies and Maras: Caviidae - Rock Cavy (kerodon Rupestris): Species Accounts  Read more: Cavies and Maras: Caviidae - Rock Cavy (kerodon Rupestris): Species Accounts|url=http://animals.jrank.org/pages/3455/Cavies-Maras-Caviidae-ROCK-CAVY-Kerodon-rupestris-SPECIES-ACCOUNTS.html|publisher=Net Industries|accessdate=30 September 2013|archive-date=2015-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412132640/http://animals.jrank.org/pages/3455/Cavies-Maras-Caviidae-ROCK-CAVY-Kerodon-rupestris-SPECIES-ACCOUNTS.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==分類==
岩豚鼠屬曾被認為是[[豚鼠亚科|豚鼠亚科]]的生物，和[[豚鼠|豚鼠]]分在一起。後來的種系發生研究顯示其關係與[[水豚|水豚]]更為接近，因此又被劃分到了[[豚鼠科|豚鼠科]]中。<ref name="rowe" />Woods 和 Kilpatrick（2005）將其分在[[水豚亞科|水豚亞科]]下，認為其在[[中新世|中新世]]中期從水豚中分化出來獨自進化。<ref>Opazo, J. C. 2005. A molecular timescale for Caviomorph rodents (Mammalia, Hystricognathi). Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution, 37:932-937.</ref>

